node.text:
Fight for what you want now, or fight against what you didn’t want forever.
What are you fighting for?

💭💭

Roll to the left, body shot
Roll to the right, body shot
jab to land the leg kick to open his stance 
Body opens up so clean cross to the body
Hook to push his angle so I’m off his line but he’s in mine
Bring his guard up with a cross up top
Hit him with body shot with the created opening.

Landed.

Take a step back, reset

Faint to read him & gain distance

He guards so I keep his guard busy up top again with a cross (setting up 2,3,2)
Ceating an opening for the body shot (3) from the other side just like last time.
Finish the combo with a cross (2,3,2)
Hard kick to make him respect your power & want to block, second kick he will try to block and creating an opening to land the teep.
Teep lands, he’s hurt and guard drops,  land in a cross to the face.
